Day 5 Spatial Intro

Chen Xing

9/29/2020

Read in ecoregion data

ca_eco <- read_sf(dsn = here("data","ca_ecoregions"), layer = "ca_eco") %>% 
  select(US_L3NAME) %>% 
  rename(region = US_L3NAME) %>% 
  st_simplify(dTolerance = 1000)

plot(ca_eco)

ggplot(data = ca_eco) + 
  geom_sf(aes(fill = region))

ca_eco <- ca_eco %>% 
  st_transform(crs = 4326)
